description:
Try Speel for yourself   https://speel.co

I tested 500 Meta ads using AI. Most of them tanked.

But 5 hook formulas kept winning across every niche, every product, every creative style.

And you can create them in under 5 minutes. No camera, no editors, no paying UGC creators $100-200 per video.

In this video I break down all 5 hooks that are crushing right now and show you exactly how to build them with AI.

If your ads aren't converting, you're probably missing one of these.
